There are various libraries used for data extraction, manipulation and visulation. Below are a few that may be useful.

# Load neccessary R Libraries

#Libraries + Environment

library(tidycensus)
library(tidyr)
library(gtools)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
library(readr)
library(formattable)
library(cowplot)
library(grid)
library(gridExtra)
